<node id="&quot;AUGMENTATION DES RETRAITES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The proposal to increase pensions is suggested to be indexed on the cost of living to enhance financial stability for retirees."</data>
