<node id="&quot;PLAFONNEMENT DES HAUTS SALAIRES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The proposal suggests capping high salaries and eliminating stock options to ensure wage equity."&lt;SEP&gt;"The proposal to cap high salaries aims to promote equity within the workforce and limit excessive compensation."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-64af714a13f88ba6b8a5c2d30baf3301</data>
