<node id="&quot;INTERDICTION DES DÉLOCALISATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A proposal to ban outsourcing to protect local jobs and industries in France."&lt;SEP&gt;"Proposal to prohibit outsourcing to protect domestic jobs and support the local economy."</data>
