  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A proposal aimed at revitalizing French industry to foster economic growth and employment."&lt;SEP&gt;"Proposal advocating for the reindustrialization of France to foster economic stability and job creation."</data>
