<node id="&quot;NATIONALISATION DES AUTOROUTES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Proposal to nationalize highways as a public asset to ensure equal access and investment in infrastructure."&lt;SEP&gt;"The call for the nationalization of highways to ensure public control over transportation infrastructure."</data>
