  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Proposal for accounting for blank votes in election results to reflect true voter sentiment."&lt;SEP&gt;"Proposal to count blank votes in elections to reflect voter sentiments and increase electoral accountability."</data>
