  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Proposal to ban double mandates, promoting the focus of politicians on their elected roles."&lt;SEP&gt;"Proposal to forbid holding multiple mandates to ensure focus and dedication in governance."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-64af714a13f88ba6b8a5c2d30baf3301</data>
